OL,3,CWater bills to rise in England and
OL,4,CWales by 6% from April
OL,6,FThe average household water bill in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales will rise by 6% to
OL,8,F#473 a year from April 1, the industry
OL,9,Fhas confirmed.
OL,11,FRegulator Ofwat says the average
OL,12,Fannual forecasted increase will be
OL,13,F#27.40 per household, equivalent to
OL,14,Fabout #2.30 a month.
OL,16,FWessex Water and Anglian Water
OL,17,Fcustomers will see the biggest rise,
OL,18,Fwith average bills set to increase to
OL,19,F#548 and #529 respectively, while
OL,20,FNorthumbrian customers will see the
OL,21,Flowest average bills of #422.
