OL,3,CWater bills to rise in England and
OL,4,CWales by 6% from April
OL,6,FThe rise comes amid public fury about
OL,7,Fsewage being discharged into Britain's
OL,8,Fwaters, and ongoing concern about
OL,9,Fshareholder bonuses amid the ongoing
OL,10,Fcost-of-living crisis.
OL,12,FBut Water UK, the trade body in charge
OL,13,Fof water companies, said there would
OL,14,Fbe support for low-income households
OL,15,Fand record investment in
OL,16,Finfrastructure to "significantly
OL,17,Freduce" the amount of sewage in rivers
OL,18,Fand seas.
