OL,3,CWater bills to rise in England and
OL,4,CWales by 6% from April
OL,6,FDavid Henderson, chief executive of
OL,7,FWater UK, said: "Next year will see
OL,8,Frecord levels of investment from water
OL,9,Fcompanies to secure the security of
OL,10,Four water supply in the future and
OL,11,Fsignificantly reduce the amount of
OL,12,Fsewage in rivers and seas.
OL,14,F"Up and down the country customers
OL,15,Fwill see the results of this
OL,16,Finvestment with more than 2,000
OL,17,Fkilometres of pipes being repaired or
OL,18,Freplaced and more capacity to treat
OL,19,Fsewage than ever before.
