OL,3,CWater bills to rise in England and
OL,4,CWales by 6% from April
OL,6,FWater UK said firms would invest a
OL,7,Frecord #14.4 billion to fund
OL,8,Fimprovements in water and sewerage
OL,9,Fsystems, and bills would automatically
OL,10,Fbe reduced by the regulator if they
OL,11,Fwere not delivered.
OL,13,FAmong the projects set to receive
OL,14,Finvestment over the coming year is
OL,15,Fthe, which will divert storm flows
OL,16,Faway from the River Thames and reduce
OL,17,Fsewage pollution into the river by 95%.
