OL,3,CWater bills to rise in England and
OL,4,CWales by 6% from April
OL,6,FWork will begin on the Havant Thicket
OL,7,Freservoir in Hampshire, the first
OL,8,Freservoir to be built in the UK for
OL,9,Fmore than 30 years.
OL,11,FWessex Water said it was investing
OL,12,Fmore than #150 million on sewage and
OL,13,Fstormwater capacity at its major water
OL,14,Frecycling centres near Bath, Bristol
OL,15,Fand Bournemouth.
OL,17,FConsumer Council for Water (CCW) chief
OL,18,Fexecutive Mike Keil said the nearly a
OL,19,Ffifth of households in England and
OL,20,FWales are already struggling to pay
OL,21,Ftheir water bills.
