OL,3,CWater bills to rise in England and
OL,4,CWales by 6% from April
OL,6,FHe said: "If water companies are
OL,7,Fserious about rebuilding trust in the
OL,8,Fsector they should use some of their
OL,9,Fprofits to help people who cannot
OL,10,Fafford another bill rise.
OL,12,F"The water industry made a commitment
OL,13,Ffive years ago to end water poverty in
OL,14,FEngland and Wales and it needs to keep
OL,15,Fthat promise.
OL,17,F"Crisis-hit households need immediate
OL,18,Frelief and the long-term security of
OL,19,Fknowing they can afford something as
OL,20,Fessential as water, without having to
OL,21,Fmake painful sacrifices."
